'''Nonagenarian''' is an [[Achievements|achievement]] of the Longevity section. The player can earn this achievement by living till the age of 90.

== Trivia ==
* This achievement is harder to obtain than [[Octogenarian (Achievement)|Octogenarian]], because [[death]] by old age can occur more frequently when the character gets older than 80 years.
* This achievement isn't directly connected to any [[ribbon]], so obtaining it doesn't guarantee a certain ribbon.
